<div class="span-24">
    <h1>Health Information</h1>
</div>

<div class="span-24">

<table>
    <caption>A display of endpoints and their health known to Mass Transit</caption>
	<tr>
	    <th>Address</th>
	    <th>First Detected At</th>
	    <th>Last Fault Detected At</th>
	</tr>
